This project is distributed under two separate licenses, depending on the
component:

- Python SDK (sdk/python/): MIT License — open source.
  See sdk/python/LICENSE.

- Backend (server / scheduler / worker, distributed as a binary or container
  image): proprietary Evaluation License — closed source, evaluation use only.
  See BACKEND-LICENSE.txt.

The backend source code is not open source and is not licensed for
redistribution. Nothing in this repository grants a license to the backend
source beyond the terms in BACKEND-LICENSE.txt.
